            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Victoriae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Augustoru</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>exercitus &amp;lt;q=C&amp;gt;ui Lau<lb break="no" n="4"/>garicione sedit <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>ites</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionarii</ex></expan> II (duo milia) DCCCLV <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Maximi</supplied>an<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> curav<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">it</supplied> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In den Felsen gehauene Platte (80 x 122 cm). Oberfläche teilweise stark verwittert. Z. 6: möglicherweise auch NV-Ligatur. Z. 7 (Ende): hinter CVR noch Reste von zwei nicht mehr eindeutig identifizierbaren Buchstaben. (B): CIL 03, 00225*; Mithoff: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
